detaileddescription.para: This project was generated with Angular CLI version 9.0.1.

sect1.title: Development server
sect1.para: Run ng serve for a dev server. Navigate to http://localhost:4200/. The app will automatically reload if you change any of the source files.

sect1.title: Code scaffolding
sect1.para: Run ng generate component component-name to generate a new component. You can also use ng generate directive|pipe|service|class|guard|interface|enum|module.

sect1.title: Build
sect1.para: Run ng build to build the project. The build artifacts will be stored in the dist/ directory. Use the --prod flag for a production build.

sect1.title: Running unit tests
sect1.para: Run ng test to execute the unit tests via Karma.

sect1.title: Running end-to-end tests
sect1.para: Run ng e2e to execute the end-to-end tests via Protractor.

sect1.title: Further help
sect1.para: To get more help on the Angular CLI use ng help or go check out the Angular CLI README.
